Time":"2019-07-16T16:46:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb9f011d917abf37f3194f0ab1b8437ead9f8200","tid":1324755,"uid":81385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84f14516b81a6b7d163e8e2948ad233e217700bf","tid":1324755,"uid":2545,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"warden加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw個熱心市民咁勁抽可以借個灣仔office出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f801aec0e08453576b2f5351cc01365ea9c0109e","tid":1324755,"uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:48:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/checkout/donate?donatePageId=5d16c3a32bd6e100016c84bd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fcheckout%2Fdonate%3FdonatePageId%3D5d16c3a32bd6e100016c84bd&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BQZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=b41d35c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/checkout/donate?donatePageId=5d16c3a32bd6e100016c84bd</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所及其香港民研計劃的成功有賴公民社會以義務工作和金錢捐助的形式給予支持。我們現在誠意向公眾人士籌集六百萬港元起動經費，以及十二萬港元贊助經費以開展香港民研的第一次民意調查專列，內容包括特首民望調查。2019年6月29 日起最先籌得的十二萬元將會用作香港民研第一次民意調查專列的經費，餘額將會撥作香港民意的起動經費。<br />\n<br />\n懇請留意所有向香港民意研究所的捐款或贊助均不能用作扣稅之用。此外，除非捐助者特別註明需以匿名形式顯示，否則有關捐助者的姓名和金額將會公開。捐款高於$10,000者，敬請預先電郵至donation.hkpop@gmail.com 通知我們。<br />\n<br />\nThe success of HKPORI and its HKPOP requires the support of our civil society both in the form of volunteerism and donations. We now seek donations for HK$6M as our startup capital, plus HK$120k public subscription to kickstart our first HKPOP omnibus survey which measures the popularity of our Chief Executive. The first $120k donations/subscriptions received on or after 29 June 2019 will be used for the omnibus survey, donations/subscriptions in access of this amount would go to the startup capital.<br />\n<br />\nPlease note that all donations and subscriptions to HKPORI are not tax deductible, and the names of donors and the amount of donation would become public information unless the donor requests for anonymity. For donations exceeding $10,000 we prefer prospective donors contacting us first at donation.hkpop@gmail.com."},{"pid":"941e231c6e0294e3eb12d2db54d83962bc93182a","tid":1324755,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8356feaf39236f45fe3165f1458ed678ad016d4","tid":1324755,"uid":204194,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:51:39.000Z","msg":"其實係香港，仲有好多香港人關心香港，但，你呢？可唔可以一齊愛護依一個咁珍貴嘅地方？<br />\n如果你有能力，幫幫需要資金嘅組織，義士基金又好，立場又好，乃至最基本蘋果3蚊有啩？<br />\n<br />\n我在此多謝你無私嘅付出！<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"fb8f5bb4d9c70b2035b788c210a8448db1db392f","tid":1324755,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":46,"score":-45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:51:54.000Z","msg":"哇屌你蔡子強廢老評論員捐得嗰一皮嘢講撚到自己大義凜然咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食屎啦"},{"pid":"900de43d174633000ef85851ad9d060b26697b74","tid":1324755,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"7ed4840be234c38e0364cf46fd19364dd9234a79","tid":1324755,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，何君堯關鍵缺席聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c4e0feb863e0cae55997b792e8743a683a73e2ac","tid":1324755,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike"